$PROBLEM From bbr: see 1000-FOCE.yaml for details
$INPUT C NUM ID TIME SEQ CMT EVID AMT DV AGE WT HT EGFR ALB BMI SEX AAG SCR AST ALT CP TAFD TAD LDOS MDV BLQ PHASE
$DATA ../../../data/derived/analysis3.csv IGNORE=(C='C', BLQ=1)
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 TRANS4
$PK
;log transformed PK parms
V2WT = LOG(WT/70) CLWT = LOG(WT/70) * 0.75 V3WT = LOG(WT/70) QWT = LOG(WT/70) * 0.75
MU_1 = THETA(1) MU_2 = THETA(2) + V2WT MU_3 = THETA(3) + CLWT MU_4 = THETA(4) + V3WT MU_5 = THETA(5) + QWT
KA = EXP(MU_1 + ETA(1)) V2 = EXP(MU_2 + ETA(2)) CL = EXP(MU_3 + ETA(3)) V3 = EXP(MU_4 + ETA(4)) Q = EXP(MU_5 + ETA(5))
S2 = V2/1000 ; dose in mcg, conc in mcg/mL
$ERROR
IPRED = F Y = IPRED * (1 + EPS(1))
$THETA ; log values (0.5) ; 1 KA (1/hr) - 1.5 (3.5) ; 2 V2 (L) - 60 (1) ; 3 CL (L/hr) - 3.5 (4) ; 4 V3 (L) - 70 (2) ; 5 Q (L/hr) - 4
$OMEGA BLOCK(3) 0.2 ;ETA(KA) 0.01 0.2 ;ETA(V2) 0.01 0.01 0.2 ;ETA(CL)
$OMEGA 0 FIX ; ETA(V3) 0 FIX ; ETA(Q)
$SIGMA 0.05 ; 1 pro error
$EST MAXEVAL=9999 METHOD=1 INTER SIGL=6 NSIG=3 PRINT=1 MSFO=./1000-FOCE.msf $COV PRINT=E $TABLE NUM CL V2 Q V3 KA ETAS(1:LAST) IPRED NPDE CWRES NOPRINT ONEHEADER FILE=1000-FOCE.tab
